Name: DIAMANTE LONG COAT
Description: This is the iconic garment of Archivio brand. The long coat is inspired by masculine tailoring, the wide and structured shoulders support the body of the satin coat. The fit is soft. Thanks to this precious fabric, this garment is made not to go unnoticed. The double-breasted lacing and the deep slit on the back combine the classic style with the contemporary one. Details: welt pockets with flap at the waist plus side pockets on the seam at the hips, peak lapel, inner welt pocket. Fully lined. Made in Italy. Dry cleaning. Main material: 100% silk. Lining: 100% polyester. The model is tall 1,75cm, she is wearing size 40.
Attribute 1 value(s): AQUA, BLACK, DARK BLUE, IVORY, LIGHT GREEN, LIGHT PINK, MAGENTA, ROSEWOOD, SILVER
